\"<book\")\n                    .contains(\"id=\\\"bk101\\\"\")\n                    .contains(\"<title>XML Developer's Guide</title>\")\n                    .contains(\"</book>\");\n        } finally {\n            executorService.shutdownNow();\n            assertThat(executorService.awaitTermination(10, TimeUnit.SECONDS)).isTrue();\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}]}
